303
00:27:02,700 --> 00:27:03,500
SONGJAM...

304
00:27:20,100 --> 00:27:22,133
P'NAPHA... I'm wondering about the original...

305
00:27:22,200 --> 00:27:23,966
The original is just that.

306
00:27:24,300 --> 00:27:26,366
