307
00:27:56,300 --> 00:27:57,100
SONGJAM!

308
00:27:57,700 --> 00:27:58,500
SONGJAM!

309
00:28:01,266 --> 00:28:02,066
SONGJAM!

310
00:29:30,566 --> 00:29:31,966
I promise

311
00:29:32,266 --> 00:29:34,300
I will try my best to be there with you.

312
00:29:34,300 --> 00:29:36,733
